Recipe Art Zine (R.A.Z.) is my first zine. 

My intention with R.A.Z. is to share my passion for the culinary arts, Recipe NFTs, and to expand the C.ollaborative, O.pensource, R.ecipe. E.conomy (C.O.R.E).  


All graphics and underlined text are clickable.

All images are linked to their source. 
If it was not possible to link their source directly, it will be listed in the references section.  


All photos that are not labeled, clickable, or listed in references, are my own photos.

All writing that is not in quotations or clickable is my own.

_______________________________


R.A.Z. will always be free to read. 

To collect, visit:  RecipeArtZine.com
